      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">When Everyone Can Ship Code, What Changes?</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 mt-4 text-base sm:text-lg leading-relaxed">We have entered a world where non-engineers can ship production code. AI coding agents handle the syntax. The bottleneck is no longer "can someone write this?" It is "does someone know what should be built and why?"</p>
